Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是废墟船 更像是废墟舰团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照正规手续派遣调查队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认是否有存活人员 查明废弃的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 开始募集调查队员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从护卫舰上征集10人 普通成员中征集若干人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 你也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能发现大宝贝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要个搬运工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我就批准吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 帅哥要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让我们帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会给你们添麻烦的 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我们就待在这里吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我的意思是留下来照看我们开来的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 船不见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫舰去进行周边调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这舰团出乎意料地大 多些帮手也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拗不过你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德你也叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人 有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是叫了 幽灵也会出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽 幽灵可以不用叫！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵是 敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要迎击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 什么都别做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 根本什么都没有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:08:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是 怎么会摊上跟你组队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下来分头行动怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就别啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从现在开始就是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吓吓雷德和艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 门关上了 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 给我等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是皮尼欧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开玩笑 开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 帅哥和艾米不就贴得更紧了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们给我适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙 认真一点探索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 莉吉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 发生什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这艘船上有过什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这个舰团
Comment: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个舰团和加尔刚蒂亚曾经有过交流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是大约7年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个舰团的船的连接方式很奇特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为连接方式是由母舰的性质决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接船自带连接臂 所以用不着人形机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是莉吉特 知道得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯托莉亚 我们可是加尔刚蒂亚的代表啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 难得得到了参观其他舰团的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算是参观学习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没必要让我们手动连接船舶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得见到了许多人 很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天教导我的利多那先生 听说是连接协会的会长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比加尔刚蒂亚的协会长年轻不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他或许确实很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉以轻心可是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怒我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这次实习没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你叫莉吉特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为未来的舰团长候补
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要再次学习船舶的连接方法了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白说来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就拜托你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以指导一下那个组怎么连接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是你们的新老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好听她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是已经全部学会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让他们见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加尔刚蒂亚流的连接技术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你教不了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就说明你学得还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于肩负责任的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经验是最宝贵的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你们舰团的做法与这里不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该也仍然有许多值得学习的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个去着手我之前说明过的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来人啊 快抬担架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你说过很危险了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利多那先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了这么多血还说没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快抬担架来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联络救护班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来看望利多那先生的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 倒也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你是在这里工作的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来进来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利多那先生 莉吉特来看你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那并不是利多那先生的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的大意 还连累你受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用内疚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒昧问一句…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个难道是照相机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你居然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我按旧世界的设计图重现出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候曾见过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能完全手工造出来 真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它还能用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐好别动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 突然跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说这个 发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…利多那先生问我要不要和他一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我从来就没考虑过要离开加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 我是个孤儿 所以去留都没有顾忌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有朋友 还有莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是我重要的人 我真不想和你们分开…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对怎样看待利多那先生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是喜欢他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你应该和他一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不想和莉吉特分开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是去是留 在加尔刚蒂亚都是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样才能结识更多的缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是难得的新缘分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的缘分？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯托莉亚 你一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是这艘母舰的动力机关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见识
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这动力机关被光虫给弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光虫？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光虫这东西呢 不仅会擅自繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且一旦结晶化就会变得非常坚硬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然都已经侵蚀到外侧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说明引擎内部肯定已经被光虫堵成硬块了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个舰团大概是依靠这个庞大的动力机关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接着许多无法独自航行的船只吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在遗留下来的大概就是这样的船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么看来 船上的人应该已经坐着能开的船离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说没有幽灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵也一起逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就当是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 调查辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和舰团长日记中的内容也一致
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 收工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 结果没宝贝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 贝罗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到什么好东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我啊 你这小气鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝壳屁股女！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的屁股！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害不害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有幽灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边可夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你害不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾 米…？
